Package towerstrategy

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Strategy
    This class provides an interface to be implemented by other classes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FarthestStrategy
    This class returns the critter with the farthest distance in the array list.
    NearestStrategy
    This class returns the critter with the nearest distance in the array list.
    StrongestStrategy
    This class returns the critter with the strongest armor and hp.
    TowerStrategy
    This class receives certain strategy parameter to execute pre-defined strategy.
    WeakestStrategy
    This class returns the critter with the weakest armor and hp.
